msgid ""
"From organizing concerts to managing ticket sales and backstage logistics, "
"Odoo offers an all-in-one solution tailored for live event venues."
msgstr ""
"Desde organizar conciertos hasta gestionar la venta de boletos y la "
"logística tras bambalinas, Odoo ofrece una solución integral diseñada para "
