"Mick, Keith, Ronnie, and the band will bring that signature Stones swagger, "
"raw power, and ageless energy that only they can deliver. No gimmicks. No "
"filler. Just timeless riffs, pounding drums, and the kind of stage presence "
"that makes history every single night."
msgstr ""
"Con un setlist compuesto de canciones icónicas como <em>Paint It Black</em>, "
"<em>Start Me Up</em>, <em>Gimme Shelter</em> y <em>Sympathy for the Devil</"
"em>, Mick, Keith, Ronnie y el resto de la banda traerán su vibra, poder y "
"energía atemporal representativas de los Stones. Sin trucos. Sin relleno. "
"Solo riffs increíbles, tambores que resuenan y el tipo de presencia escénica "
"que hará cada noche histórica."

